cb:div.p:
New Year’s Day, ascending the hall: Today I wish to speak the Buddha Dharma for the beginning of the year, but Jingqing has already spoken it;



wishing to speak the phrase of non-movement, it has again been spoken by Fachang. Unavoidably, I will just speak according to the present situation



for all of you. He struck the staff once and said: Three sections differ, yet are gathered into the highest category.

Thanking Ming, the scripture repository master, ascending the hall: The nostrils of the patriarchs and the claws and fangs from of old—if you understand, then affairs are of one family;



if you do not understand, then there are countless differences. Just as scriptures return to the canon and Chan returns to the sea—how do you understand this? Bian



jade is without flaw, and yet it has flaws.

Bathing the Buddha, ascending the hall: When body, speech, and mind are pure, it is called the Buddha’s appearance in the world—yet the face is full of dust;



when body, speech, and mind are not pure, it is called the Buddha’s passing into extinction—yet the whole body is mud and water. If you clearly understand this, there is no repayment of grace



that can be made. If not, even exhausting the waters of the Jian River cannot wash it clean. Why? Water does not wash water.

So-and-so, from illumination comes sincerity, from sincerity comes illumination. The lifeblood of the Master, the eyes of Yangqi. Thus,



if you understand, it is a ten-thousand-mile journey. Right now, cut off the lips and tongue—speak quickly, speak quickly. He throws down the torch,



saying: the fire boy of Bingding comes seeking fire.
